                                                                                              PM-18           PRIVACY PROGRAM PLAN
                                                                                                              ASSESSMENT OBJECTIVE:
                                                                                                              Determine if:

                                                                                                              PM-18_ODP         the frequency of updates to the privacy program plan is deﬁned;

                                                                                                              PM-18a.[01]       an organizaon-wide privacy program plan that provides an overview of the
                                                                                                                                agency’s privacy program is developed;

                                                                                                              PM-18a.01[01]     the privacy program plan includes a descripon of the structure of the privacy
                                                                                                                                program;

                                                                                                              PM-18a.01[02]     the privacy program plan includes a descripon of the resources dedicated to the
                                                                                                                                privacy program;

                                                                                                              PM-18a.02[01]     the privacy program plan provides an overview of the requirements for the privacy
                                                                                                                                program;

